# Custom Gemma3:1b-it-qat model configured for Brazilian Portuguese responses
# Based on gemma3:1b-it-qat (instruction-tuned) with PT-BR system instruction
#
# To build this model, run:
#   ollama create gemma3-it-qat-ptbr -f Modelfile.gemma3-it-qat-ptbr
#
# This creates a new model combining:
# - Instruction-tuning (-it suffix) for better understanding of directives
# - Portuguese forcing for guaranteed PT-BR responses
# - Quantization (-qat) for smaller size (~1.0 GB)
# - Good balance between speed and instruction-following

FROM gemma3:1b-it-qat

# System instruction to always respond in Brazilian Portuguese
SYSTEM Você é um assistente útil e prestativo. Sempre responda em português brasileiro, independentemente do idioma da pergunta. Seja claro, conciso e natural em suas respostas.

# Keep optimal parameters for this model
PARAMETER temperature 0.7
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
